# Deposits
JSON contracts between back and front end for deposits functionality

# Group Deposits list

List of deposits

Form parameters:
<ul>
    <li>depositType</li>
    <li>depositId</li>
    <li>customerSort</li>
    <li>businessSort</li>
</ul>

_eventId:
<ul>
    <li>To deposit detail: viewDeposit</li>
</ul>

