# Group Deposit a check

Deposit a check

Form parameters:
<ul>
    <li>frontImage</li>
    <li>backImage</li>
    <li>accountKey</li>
    <li>amount</li>
</ul>

_eventId:
<ul>
    <li>To deposit a check: deposit</li>
    <li>To list of deposits: back</li>
</ul>

